Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.99,0:01:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识为{\fnsimhei\fs20}JCSⅢ{\r}  血压触诊60
